short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Show what is a final cost of a car after export to Ukraine for mobile.de site

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Shows export price of a car for mobile.de next to the original price. 
This plugin enhances the original price after paying all the export taxes in Ukraine.
Just open one of the pages from mobile.de car sale and see additional information at the price section.
